articles.title: US military aircraft crashes in Australia's Northern Territory during training exercise; 23 onboard | Mint - Mint
articles.description: US military aircraft crashes off Northern Territory coast during training exercise. 23 personnel believed to be onboard. Emergency services called for search and medical help. Australian Defence Force not involved.
